{
  "stem": "10588.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "For the first time in my life-- I came from a home where I was very modest, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I wasn't wearing slacks at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I never undressed, even from my own parents in front, since when I was already little older, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And here you had to disrobe completely naked before strangers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Some girls had their monthly cycle and nothing to shield themselves with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then they shaved us all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "All of a sudden, our past was gone, everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we went into the shower.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We went to one place and went out to another.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "There was a whole mountain of striped clothes, which was the lager. 'Lager' means camp-- concentration camp, except that was not a concentration.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It was a killing center where-- death factory, because I came to Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But there was Auschwitz, and there was Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And Birkenau had crematoriums and, and gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we were given those clothes, and we put on-- the same number that we had on the arm was sewn on here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "From then on, I was no longer Itka.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I became number two, five, six, seven, three.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Except-- each time they called my number, I was so angry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And under my breath, I would say-- under my breath, I used to say 'Itka.' Maybe to you, I'm a number, but I'm not.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I will never-- I cannot [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "I'm Itka.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I remember distinctly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Each time when they said it, I said, no, I will never see myself through your eyes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And with each guard, they had in another pile, wooden clogs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Some were fortunate that they got a matching pair.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I was not so fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I had an unmatched pair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And we got an enamel bowl.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
